Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Door God 1', 3: 'These things are weak, but they just keep coming.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Door God 2', 3: 'If you have the time to bark, just fight harder. Monsters have gone through.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Door God 1', 3: "What? I'm not slacking... Hey, Door God 3! Don't fall asleep!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Door God 3', 3: "I said I didn't want to work overtime...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Door God 4', 3: "We'll take care of this place. You go inside first.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Door God 4', 3: "You are welcome. It's our duty to keep these monsters outside the door.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Door God 4', 3: "Don't worry, they can't hurt us.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Door God 1', 3: 'Yep, just relax... Whoa! Watch it, Door God 2! You almost hit me!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'You know you can always trust them.'}
{3: 'Without hesitation, you push the door open and get sucked in.'}
